Make the INCLUDE_PATH argument work correctly

Hello, I'm NAKAGAWA Masaki (PAUSE ID: MASAKI).

I'm using Catalyst::View::Templated.

Today, I use it with View's local config();

    package MyApp::View::MyTemplate;
    use parent 'Catalyst::View::Templated';
    __PACKAGE__->config(
        INCLUDE_PATH => ['/path/to/my/includes'],
    );

    (snip)
    my $view = $c->view('MyTemplate');

After I look $view->{INCLUDE_PATH} and hope ['/path/to/my/includes'],
however this value is ['/path/to/MyApp/root']. It's C::V::Templated's
default value.

So I wrote patch and tests for this issue, and patch is attached.

I'm very sorry for my poor English;

Thank you.

